# Blender laptop sway loop: 119 MB of deterministic output from
# scratch/laptop.py. Regenerate with `blender -b -P scratch/laptop.py`
# (about an hour) rather than carrying it in history.
# feed.mp4 and loop.mp4 are NOT ignored on purpose: the SFX frame
# constants in src/Composition.tsx are pinned to exact timestamps
# inside those files, so re-recording them means re-pinning by hand.
